# ── TEMPORARY: fixed L74 design lookup keyed on effective HRR (L68) ──
# Established from ~18 VB reference .evc decks across three tunnels (one-way
# 2- and 3-lane, plus a two-way tunnel), both traffic states, lengths
# 320–497.6 m, mixes 78–86% car: L74 depends ONLY on the effective HRR
# written to L68 — invariant to length, lane count, direction,
# NORMAL/CONGEST, per-deck fdb and traffic mix. This supersedes the (A,B,K)
# multiplier for these classes (that 3-point fit mis-predicts 15 MW:
# formula 5106, VB 4009). The formula is kept as a fallback for any HRR not
# in the table (e.g. 50 MW).
